Word SSP Representation The remarks fields are Markup multiline, which enables the text to be formatted. This requires special handling. See Section 2.5.3 Markup-line and Markup-multiline Fields in OSCAL, or visit:
https://pages.nist.gov/OSCAL/documentation/schema/datatypes/#markup-multiline Queries are for the Interconnection Security Agreement (ISA)'s remote POC and AO information. To obtain the ISA's local POC and AO information:
Replace &quot;isa-poc-remote&quot; with &quot;isa-poc-local&quot;
Replace &quot;[isa-authorizing-official-remote&quot; with &quot;isa-authorizing-official-local&quot;
